Gladys Ndonyi aka G-Class a mụrụ Gladys Nd autonom Tantoh, na July 1975) bụ onye ọchụnta ego na onye isi ihe nkiri Cameroon bụ onye guzobere na onye isi oche ugbu a nke UK Cameroon Film and movie Academy na onye isi nke G-Classe Entertainment. N'afọ 2016, ọ nwetara nhọpụta abụọ maka onye na-akwalite ihe nkiri Africa kachasị mma na UK na Afro Hollywood Award na 20th African Film Awards.

Enweghị ozi gbasara ụbọchị ọmụmụ Gladys Ndonyi, ọ na-egosi na amụrụ ya na July 1975. A mụrụ ya na Cameroon ma kwaga na UK, [mgbe?] wee gụọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Mahadum Greenwich na mmepụta ihe nkiri na London Film Academy, ma e wezụga ntụrụndụ, ọ bụ onye ọrụ ahụike.
Gladys Ndonyi bụ onye isi ntụrụndụ, ọ dịghị ihe e bipụtara banyere afọ ọ malitere ọrụ ya

A maara ya maka ọrụ ya iji kwalite ihe nkiri nke Cameroon site na ịmepụta Cameroon Film and Movie Academy Awards na ntụrụndụ G-class n'afọ 2015.
N'afọ 2016, ọ nwetara nhọpụta abụọ maka onye na-akwalite ihe nkiri Africa kachasị mma na UK na Afro Hollywood Award na 20th African Film Awards.
